Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.45,0:00:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.41,0:00:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worried that this full tank of energy will lose it's destination
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.68,0:00:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoever shakes for just a minute their boredom, will explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.82,0:00:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I ride, atop the white line, Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sit down, in the place you have faith Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.91,0:00:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go to the place that tempts you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.30,0:00:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If each person took one thing at a time, freedom and passion in their hand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the shine to come, continue our journey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.70,0:00:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unclear everyday trump-card that sustains me, is your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.89,0:01:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The best growth is coming forth, unstoppable wild drive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.95,0:01:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are both yet to settle down, striking the door
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.44,0:01:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Noah, no matter how powerful the Monster you try and attack me with is,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.20,0:01:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and regardless of how many Life Points you have,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.04,0:01:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so long as I have the bonds I share with my friends, I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.60,0:01:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You use your power to force people's hearts into accepting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.15,0:01:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll never be beaten by someone like you who uses such brazen methods!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So take {\b0}this{\b1}, Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.91,0:01:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is our power of cooperation!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.21,0:01:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Darkness of the Kaiba Family"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.75,0:02:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.35,0:02:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.18,0:02:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.65,0:02:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since our bodies are back to normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0} won, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Yugi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Yugi took over your deck and fought Noah in a Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.28,0:02:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi took my deck...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.35,0:03:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I at least surpassed Seto in the end, didn't I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.15,0:03:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.11,0:03:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seto {\b0}chose{\b1} defeat\N in order to save Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.72,0:03:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then I lost to Yugi, who took over Seto's spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The "bonds of friendship", was it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.25,0:03:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've always... I've always been alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.55,0:03:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is {\i1}that{\i0} why I lost?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.01,0:03:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's so...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was because I didn't have any {\i1}friends{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.25,0:03:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't accept that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.20,0:03:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DON'T LOOK AT ME LIKE THAT!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.95,0:04:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is how it is, I'll just take over your personality and {\i1}become{\i0} you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.98,0:04:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's with... these visions...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is... this man with that serious expression...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.08,0:04:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what... is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.85,0:04:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell {\i1}are{\i0} you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you've really pissed me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.54,0:04:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off, brother!\N This is a kid you're picking a fight with!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.59,0:04:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now let us all out of here immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And before you do that, give me back my real body! OOH-AH!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your "real body"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.12,0:05:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your real bodies aren't even {\i1}here{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Your"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.93,0:05:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.39,0:05:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still haven't figured it out yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything you see here is {\i1}virtual{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's not a real thing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I get it! That's why all the pain we get here feels real!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of your real bodies are being held in Virtual Simulator Capsules.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I saw something similar when Noah entered my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.04,0:05:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is that what he meant?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking something was strange for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's peculiar that we could actually get hurt in Virtual Space.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.07,0:05:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.91,0:05:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we all just lost consciousness back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just transferred your minds to the Virtual Simulator.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.16,0:05:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm disappointed in you, Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! That voice...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.45,0:06:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gozaburo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father, why are you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have passed away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.42,0:06:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.22,0:06:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that my body has been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my mind has lived on\N and escaped death!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used the same system I tested on Noah,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.33,0:06:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and became the ultimate being after being transferred into the computer, in a sense reviving as a virtual being.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph. No matter what form you take, you're still the same disgusting man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wanting to\N see you so badly, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been alone here for so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I no longer have any use for {\i1}you{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.96,0:06:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Noah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, enough with the chit chat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.85,0:06:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why don't you enlighten us, Gozaburo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.61,0:06:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the foolish plan you've got cooked up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.82,0:07:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph, you're just as patronizing as always, Seto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.96,0:07:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. I will tell you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It all started out with an honest desire to save my dieing son, Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah was born to inherit my very mind, to be the runner of Kaiba Corporation and control the entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.96,0:07:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as you can imagine, it created quite a {\i1}problem{\i0} for my plans when he went and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.89,0:07:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Created quite a problem for my plans when he went and died"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How cruel...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end, virtual is virtual.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.99,0:07:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nowhere near the same as living like a normal person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But how many people would survive after this plan of yours was commenced?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}About 3%, more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't you think that's a bit too little?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't really care.\N It has nothing to do with me, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.33,0:07:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shortly after, I realized something about the Virtual World and the Real World.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For someone such as myself who lived in in this reality, the Real World, the gap between the two of us was vast.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:07:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.53,0:08:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just trying to make you happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, Seto...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You appeared before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.39,0:08:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you adopted me as a {\i1}test{\i0} for Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if Noah won, it would be the proof you needed that Virtual Reality surpassed Reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You adopted me in order to help Noah prove himself greater than I!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.55,0:08:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph. How wrong you are, Seto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were meant to be\N Noah's {\i1}container{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah's... {\i1}container{\i0}... you said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.54,0:08:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly. After realizing first hand the limitations of Virtual Reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.42,0:08:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sought to bring Noah back to life in a body of his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Seto, you were the one I selected for that task!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.82,0:08:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... not something a {\i1}real{\i0} human being would think of!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.91,0:08:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This man called Gozaburo...\N Now I understand why Kaiba hates him so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.68,0:08:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despise me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that didn't go\N as I had planned either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't forgive you for snatching Kaiba Corporation straight from right under my nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.80,0:09:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So before killing myself, I transfered all of my memories into the computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was at that moment that I decided you would no longer be a test for Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I plan to steal your disgraceful body from you, and revive once again as the runner of Kaiba Corporation!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.35,0:09:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way... So you're saying I was just being used...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.07,0:09:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.45,0:09:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to Seto, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have to hate anyone, hate Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.96,0:09:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scumbag!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I no longer have any need for your body either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because, regardless of whether I have a body or not, I can easily hack into Kaiba Corporation's computer network.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.54,0:09:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Within a matter of seconds, the world would be in the palms of my hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.39,0:09:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph, what a {\i1}joke{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.39,0:09:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even have a {\i1}body{\i0} anymore.\N What could you possibly do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.27,0:09:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.29,0:10:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An advanced group of artillery Kaiba Corporation built in our secret base after signing a certain contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.39,0:10:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satellite missiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Missiles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.95,0:10:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Originally, this mobile floating fortress was built as the launching site for this type of weaponry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.67,0:10:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has weapons aimed at every major city in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father, are you saying that you were able to hack into the system that controls it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.91,0:10:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so surprised aver this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.92,0:10:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it not {\i1}you{\i0}, Noah, who gave me this idea in the first place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.10,0:10:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.06,0:10:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I made a simulation of something interesting not too long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.82,0:10:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I calculated that if we used the entire financial resources and weaponry of Kaiba Corporation,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}we could destroy the entire world in just 30 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.14,0:10:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet you didn't know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.77,0:10:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:11:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I plan to remain as a virtual existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using computer mainframes around the entire world, I can gain control over the entire world with almost no effort!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As we spoke, I have taken control of this world's program.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.85,0:11:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All exits connecting the Real World and the Virtual World have been shut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.33,0:11:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of you people will be leaving this Virtual World ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of you had better put aside your differences and get along well together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will live immortal, never feeling pain or hunger again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.12,0:11:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can almost view this place as a Heavenly paradise!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba Corporation belongs to {\i1}me{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give it to {\i1}anyone{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.48,0:11:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Gozaburo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.19,0:12:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an exit in this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.24,0:12:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father was right.\N All the exits have been closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.75,0:12:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning to get a body and return to the Real World.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was then going to run Kaiba Corporation in Seto's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.28,0:12:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was just doing what Father wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.41,0:12:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... Father said he no longer needs me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was exactly the same when we came to his home...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was just being used by Gozaburo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's no exits, we'll be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there really no other way to return to the Real World?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.93,0:13:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If not, I'll remain trapped in the body of a monkey {\i1}forever{\i0}! OOH-AH~!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's the deal, Noah?\N You sure there aren't any other exits?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite a shame, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may get off fooling that deadbeat over there, but you can't fool {\i1}me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father has locked the program.\N We can't create another exit from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you all give up on leaving and stay here in this world with me as my father suggested?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.07,0:13:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more fun than it looks...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.84,0:13:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you're still saying that!\N You were abandoned by Gozaburo, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.19,0:13:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts, Mokuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No! He's not my big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.21,0:13:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.59,0:13:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the long face, Mokuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.76,0:14:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He put us through so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But when I look at him, I can't help but think of how Big brother was back in the old days!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.38,0:14:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.76,0:14:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There may still be one more chance to get back to the Real World.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.65,0:14:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.65,0:14:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that one exit I\N made myself is still active...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hid it inside one of a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm almost positive my father wouldn't know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it? Hurry and take us there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.40,0:14:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it can't be helped.\N Just follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't let things end like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.58,0:14:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If this is how things will go, I'll get myself a body and return to the Real World, no matter what I have to do to get one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.88,0:14:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How {\i1}amusing{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.24,0:15:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tch, weaker than I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba, I have something to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About what Noah said.\N How much of it do you trust?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, here I thought you were going to ask something more serious with that look on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.77,0:15:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel as if he's planning something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that well on my own without {\i1}you{\i0} telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't think he's doing anything bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.06,0:15:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.06,0:15:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just don't think Noah would be plotting anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.79,0:15:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Noah said himself he was just being used by his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.84,0:16:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And knowing that, do you really think Noah would have a reason to try something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true. You could be right about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.53,0:16:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now isn't it about time we switch places?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.73,0:16:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's inside here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behind this gate lies Virtual Domino City.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Virtual Domino City?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where'd everyone...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.92,0:16:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.71,0:16:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.05,0:16:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did everyone go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.97,0:16:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is where you were?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah! Where's the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They went ahead already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.41,0:16:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, come this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.83,0:16:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As we speak, they're all lost in the flow of their own memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.12,0:17:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess who?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.29,0:17:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck {\i1}is{\i0} this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.31,0:17:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's low, Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.44,0:17:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.32,0:17:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Osiris, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.99,0:17:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super Conductor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thunder Force!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.20,0:17:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He counter-attacks with Dragon Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't win...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't... defeat Osiris...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.27,0:17:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a door leading to the Real World in this game center.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.93,0:18:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe there's an {\i1}arcade{\i0} in the Virtual World!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.32,0:18:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry Mokuba, but I'll be taking your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.62,0:18:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.05,0:18:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? We'll be caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otogi! Take Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0} and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.56,0:18:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.90,0:18:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've still got business with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.65,0:18:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just run away already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, this way, Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let em escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.30,0:18:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.94,0:18:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! That's dangerous, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.07,0:18:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So where do you wanna go, Jounouchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.25,0:18:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.29,0:18:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anywhere's fine, so long as it's with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.94,0:19:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the very beginning, I've always thought of you as...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.79,0:19:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! This isn't really happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.23,0:19:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.41,0:19:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.75,0:19:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That Noah bastard's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.26,0:19:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s gone too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Noah... About what you said earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.03,0:20:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we return to the Real World, you're going to need a body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.50,0:20:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But your body is gone already, right...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And {\b0}that's{\b1} why I'll be taking {\b0}your{\b1} body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.07,0:20:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you promise me that you'll stop trying to hurt my big brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.91,0:20:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be happy to ask\N my brother a favor for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.13,0:20:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To get you a new body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.35,0:20:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't be able to get you a real body or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But with Kaiba Corporation's technology, we can make some pretty good-looking androids!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.92,0:20:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything, it won't be a monkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, we're brothers and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.60,0:20:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't believe he'd call me his {\b0}brother{\b1} after all those horrible things I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.16,0:20:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a simpleton.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.41,0:20:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, this isn't the time to be playing games.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the exit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My big brother and the others are there already, aren't they Noah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.19,0:20:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The exit should be in that game over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.87,0:21:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way Gozaburo would know about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.88,0:21:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.10,0:21:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally got one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.48,0:21:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A living flesh-and-blood body!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.11,0:21:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't virtual!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.87,0:21:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a {\i1}real{\i0} body!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.61,0:21:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're still trapped inside of Virtual Domino City.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.62,0:21:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our only chance of escape, Noah, is nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.13,0:21:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we can't find Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} and Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0} either!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} headed by himself to settle things with his father?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.36,0:21:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While we search the streets for Noah, a hoard of Monsters appear!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.99,0:22:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez! Just hurry up and let us return to the Real World already!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.30,0:22:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.05,0:22:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Exodia Necross"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.39,0:22:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.37,0:22:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, wherever it rises
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.28,0:22:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A dream is a dream, and it won't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.55,0:22:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The straight rail and the steep route
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.23,0:22:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To go, or not go all of yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.62,0:22:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm getting tired of counting my advances in a cage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.18,0:22:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Respect! Boys, show me your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.77,0:22:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's awkward, but draw the map
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.54,0:23:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now let's walk forever with our head up high...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.69,0:23:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, if it starts to get to familiar like you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.50,0:23:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}answer freely to the everyday discomfort
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.28,0:23:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to believe you, because I am losing my way with everything
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.26,0:23:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hiding in my heart... this secret paradise
